      "span_text": "The study began with 147 male, 4-week-old C57BL/ 6J mice and 162 homozygous for the Apoe tm1Unc mutation (apoE-deficient mice) backcrossed 10 times to C57BL/6J mice, obtained from The Jackson Laboratory  ).",
